textAnnotations.description:
Soybean Gheese
Instant
FROMAGE DE SOJA Instantané
速食
花是用黄豆和糖制成的纯
種食品。本品可即食、美味可
ロ、常 富,老少皆宜,可作早
点一 日常随时食用。
食法:第一包豆腐花(32克)
剑入中,加入200毫升85℃的开
用质點定向搜拌一金儿。然后
里5-10分钟便自然地凝结成
This product, soybean cheese, 100%
vegetal, is made of soybean and ca
nesuger. Instant, delicious and nut
tive, it can be appreciated by aduts
as by children and consumed for
breaktast or at all moment in a whole
day.
Direction for use: Dissolve the con
ents of one packet (32g in a bowl
with 200 ml hot water above 85C
stir it directively with a spoon for a
while. Then let it to be immovable
and 5-10 minutes later, it will be
naturally condensed into soybean
cheese. That's all
Net weight 32g (1.120 ou)
Ingredient Vegetal protein, dired
extract of soybean and cane-sugar.
Exporters Guangxi Cereals Ols and
Foodstuffs Import and Export (W
zhou) Corporation
Address: 122 X0jiang 4 Road.
Wuzhou, Guangad, ChinaPre)
Tel: (86-0774)2026915

净重:32克(1.128安士)。
成份:植物蛋自,黄豆和茂糖。
